Sorry. We'll talk later.

19:05.944 --> 19:08.708
You should play with him. He misses you.

19:08.780 --> 19:11.146
<i>'Cause she thinks she's the passionate one</i>

19:11.216 --> 19:12.308
<i>Oh, yeah! It was like lightning</i>

19:12.384 --> 19:14.818
Is that cotton candy? Nice.

19:14.887 --> 19:16.149
