and Lindsey and not us and...

20:24.323 --> 20:25.915
Yes, Jamie? What?

20:25.991 --> 20:27.219
I wanna play <i>Rock Band.</i>

20:27.292 --> 20:29.783
Well, go play, then, sweetie. Go on.

20:31.396 --> 20:33.364
<i>And the man in the back said</i>
<i>'Everyone attack'</i>

20:33.432 --> 20:35.457
<i>And it turned into a ballroom blitz</i>

20:35.534 --> 20:37.502
<i>And the girl in the corner said</i>
<i>'Boy, I wanna warn you'</i>

20:37.569 --> 20:38.968
