if Brooke had that rule.

21:29.354 --> 21:33.154
I gotta say, man, I'm a little jealous
of everyone's success.

21:33.825 --> 21:35.952
Why didn't you ever call me?

21:36.028 --> 21:38.326
- I would have helped you.
- I know.

21:38.397 --> 21:40.024
That's why I didn't.

21:40.098 --> 21:42.931
Well, is there anything
I can do for you now, Rachel?

21:43.035 --> 21:44.297
Anything?

21:45.070 --> 21:46.162
