21:57.115 --> 21:58.275
A little natural high.

21:58.350 --> 22:00.113
- Rachel, I...
- Come on.

22:00.185 --> 22:02.449
You slept with your boss.
How about a model?

22:02.521 --> 22:03.749
I can't.

22:06.325 --> 22:09.852
- I'm sorry. I must look terrible.
- Don't.

22:09.928 --> 22:12.055
You're beautiful,
and you could have whoever you want

22:12.130 --> 22:14.462
- and whatever you want.
- But?

22:14.533 --> 22:16.626
But you don't believe that.

22:18.003 --> 22:19.800
You need to learn to
let go of whatever it is

22:19.871 --> 22:21.668
that makes you think
you're not good enough.

22:21.740 --> 22:24.300
'Cause that's when you're gonna beat this.

22:24.376 --> 22:25.900
When you learn that you matter.

22:31.583 --> 22:33.175
I should go.

22:36.521 --> 22:40.252
<i>Safe inside my mind I hide...</i>

22:41.993 --> 22:45.986
<i>Safe inside my mind I hide...</i>

22:52.537 --> 22:57.474
<i>Safe inside my mind I hide...</i>

23:03.615 --> 23:05.310
(KNOCKING ON DOOR)

23:05.884 --> 23:07.408
Can we come in?

23:11.523 --> 23:14.356
- What you got there, little man?
- Nothing.

23:15.494 --> 23:17.485
That's more than nothing.

23:18.130 --> 23:21.429
Those are the two people who love you
the most in the world.

23:21.500 --> 23:23.400
Almost as much as I do.

23:25.070 --> 23:26.867
Is he your boyfriend?

23:28.540 --> 23:31.270
You're the only boyfriend in my life.

23:31.343 --> 23:33.937
Hey. I heard I owe you one.

23:34.012 --> 23:36.003
You got me another chance with Brooke.

23:36.081 --> 23:39.414
What's under all the clothes,
Brooke Davis?

23:39.484 --> 23:41.076
So, you find out?

23:43.922 --> 23:47.289
On that note, boy time is over. Let's go.

23:47.359 --> 23:48.986
Give me your knuckles.

23:49.094 --> 23:51.619
<i>(SUPERSTAR</i> BY LUPE FIASCO
PLAYING ON SOUNDTRACK)

23:51.696 --> 23:53.721
<i>The world brought me to my knees</i>
<i>What have you brung you?</i>

23:53.799 --> 23:57.997
Hey. Look, I hope you don't feel
too slighted by the setup.

23:58.069 --> 24:00.594
To be honest, I kind of expected it
from you guys.

24:00.672 --> 24:03.266
You being you and Lindsey.

24:05.510 --> 24:07.842
Your hearts
were in the right place, though.

24:07.913 --> 24:10.780
You picked the right person to
spend the rest of your life with, Luke.

24:13.585 --> 24:14.950
So did you.

24:15.020 --> 24:16.146
<i>I battle with it well</i>

24:16.221 --> 24:18.781
<i>Though I need a holiday</i>
<i>like lady who sung blue</i>

24:18.857 --> 24:21.189
<i>Go back</i>
<i>Whatever you did, you undo</i>

24:21.259 --> 24:23.625
<i>Heavy as heaven</i>
<i>The devil owe me two tons, too</i>

24:23.695 --> 24:27.358
<i>If you are what you say you are</i>

24:27.432 --> 24:29.525
<i>A superstar</i>

24:29.601 --> 24:32.001
So this is kind of weird, huh?

24:32.370 --> 24:34.770
Then again, I did find you pretty cute
back in high school.

24:34.840 --> 24:37.775
- Oh, God, come on.
- I did.

24:37.843 --> 24:41.040
But I was with Brooke,
and you were with Lucas.

24:42.047 --> 24:43.776
You still love him?

24:44.983 --> 24:46.814
He's with Lindsey now.

24:48.253 --> 24:50.278
<i>Down through the basement</i>
<i>Past the Indian graves</i>

24:50.355 --> 24:51.652
<i>Where the dinosaurs laid</i>

24:51.723 --> 24:54.055
<i>And out through China</i>
<i>Nearly misses airliners</i>

24:54.559 --> 24:55.787
Chase, I...

24:55.861 --> 24:57.192
Three o'clock.

24:57.262 --> 24:59.093
Lucas was looking.

25:02.334 --> 25:04.461
Just trying to help you out.

25:05.070 --> 25:06.901
<i>We want it to braid</i>

25:06.972 --> 25:09.497
<i>Meaning we want it to grow</i>
<i>Meaning we want it to stay</i>

25:09.574 --> 25:12.372
Hey. Did I miss all the fun?

25:12.978 --> 25:14.377
I guess not.

25:15.814 --> 25:19.614
When I was a little girl, I sprayed the boys
I liked most with Wacky String.

25:19.684 --> 25:23.142
But then Todd Pinkerton got some
in his mouth, and he started to cry.

25:23.221 --> 25:25.485
Needless to say, I abandoned that tactic.

25:28.360 --> 25:30.385
I really like you, Marvin.

25:31.062 --> 25:34.520
So the next time you go to visit
some really hot former model

25:34.599 --> 25:40.265
who you have some sort of sexual history
with and who's in a vulnerable state,

25:40.338 --> 25:41.737
just consider me.

25:43.275 --> 25:45.607
You're right. I can do that.

25:49.014 --> 25:51.539
So I built it up so much.
I told all these kids that my mom

25:51.616 --> 25:56.781
was gonna get me this cake with Rambo
on it, like, chest scars, flames, you know?

25:56.855 --> 26:00.518
My mom brings the cake out,
and instead of a picture of Rambo,

26:00.592 --> 26:04.892
it's, like, this dinky homemade cake.
No Rambo, just the words,

26:04.963 --> 26:08.421
"Rambo says happy birthday"
scribbled across the top.

26:08.700 --> 26:10.361
So embarrassing.

26:11.570 --> 26:14.437
Well, I thought it was funny,
but if you have a better story...

26:14.506 --> 26:17.134
No, your mom sounds sweet.

26:17.208 --> 26:19.699
On the rare occasion that my mother
ever actually remembered my birthday,

26:19.778 --> 26:23.407
she'd just toss her gold card at me
and tell me to go buy something.

26:24.049 --> 26:25.573
She never really cared to get involved.

26:25.650 --> 26:28.244
She's not exactly the nurturing type.

26:32.190 --> 26:34.124
Hey, junkie.

26:34.192 --> 26:35.955
Get up.

26:36.628 --> 26:41.793
You and Peyton are like bloodsucking
vermin that just won't go away.

26:43.001 --> 26:44.764
Where's my daughter?

26:45.136 --> 26:46.933
She's at a party.

26:47.005 --> 26:48.370
Of course she is.

26:48.440 --> 26:50.032
And when she's not partying
with the bartender,

26:50.108 --> 26:52.269
she's running a halfway house, apparently.

26:52.344 --> 26:56.110
I'm not... I'm better now.

26:56.181 --> 26:58.445
Yeah. Whatever.

26:58.516 --> 27:01.383
Today you're fine,
tomorrow you'll have pawned my Pradas.

27:01.453 --> 27:03.444
It's different this time.

27:04.222 --> 27:05.689
Brooke believes in me.

27:05.757 --> 27:09.318
Oh, well, look out Tony Robbins,
here comes my daughter.

27:10.762 --> 27:13.856
You know, I convinced her
to cut you loose once.

27:14.466 --> 27:16.263
I can do it again.

27:16.334 --> 27:18.564
Brooke wouldn't do that to me.

27:18.970 --> 27:19.994
No?

27:23.041 --> 27:24.702
Look at you.

27:24.776 --> 27:26.641
You're pathetic.

27:26.711 --> 27:29.805
And the sad thing is, you're gonna
lie to yourself long enough

27:29.881 --> 27:32.281
to hurt the people who still give a damn.

27:32.350 --> 27:35.945
Why don't you think of them
before you relapse

27:36.021 --> 27:38.546
and waste all their time and their money?

27:40.759 --> 27:43.785
I mean, let's be honest.

27:44.462 --> 27:46.487
You can't beat this thing.

27:48.967 --> 27:53.063
And deep down inside, you know it, too.

27:54.372 --> 27:55.703
Don't you?

28:16.761 --> 28:19.195
No! No! No! No! No!

28:19.297 --> 28:22.061
Get him! Get him! Get him!
Get him! Get him!

28:24.169 --> 28:25.727
One, two, three.

28:25.804 --> 28:29.035
Boom. Boom.

28:31.876 --> 28:33.901
Guys, can you take it easy, please?

28:33.978 --> 28:36.378
Be careful. Come on, sweetie,
it's time to go.

28:36.448 --> 28:38.075
- But, Mom.
- It's getting late.

28:38.149 --> 28:41.175
You got to go to bed soon, all right?
You got to remember his size.

28:41.252 --> 28:44.278
You treat him like one of the guys,
but he's just a little boy.

28:44.355 --> 28:46.323
Look, Haley, I don't want to disrespect

28:46.391 --> 28:49.155
'cause I know you and Nathan
going through some things right now,

28:49.227 --> 28:52.321
but I never lost sight
on how little that boy is.

28:52.397 --> 28:56.458
Actually, I'm amazed how little he is
because his heart is so big.

28:56.601 --> 29:01.265
You know, today all he wanted to do was
make sure y'all was a whole family again.

29:01.339 --> 29:03.637
That's what today meant to him.

29:04.709 --> 29:10.079
And if you hadn't noticed, I just think y'all
are the ones that done lost sight of things.

29:21.459 --> 29:23.222
<i>(OPEN LA TEBY</i> RYAN LINDSEY
PLAYING ON SOUNDTRACK)

29:27.599 --> 29:30.397
I can't believe we're getting married.

29:30.468 --> 29:31.560
