29:31.636 --> 29:34.605
After the wedding,
there'll be another Scott in Tree Hill.

29:34.672 --> 29:36.902
You think you can handle that?

29:38.309 --> 29:40.937
Who said I was taking your last name?

29:42.447 --> 29:45.041
So how's our little plan working out?

29:46.818 --> 29:48.581
They're talking.

29:49.621 --> 29:51.486
That's a start, right?

29:55.627 --> 29:59.358
Look, I just wanted to say I'm sorry.

30:01.199 --> 30:03.190
