PLAYING ON SOUNDTRACK)

31:07.198 --> 31:08.256
Hey.

31:11.069 --> 31:13.367
Thanks for all your help
with the party, man.

31:13.438 --> 31:16.134
- Sure.
- The Moonbounce was the bomb,

31:16.207 --> 31:18.402
and the cotton candy was off the chain.

31:18.476 --> 31:21.172
- Them was all your ideas.
