31:35.360 --> 31:38.591
But that's where I draw the line.
I ain't never have a pet.

31:38.663 --> 31:41.291
Just pet him, scaredy. He doesn't bite.

31:48.239 --> 31:49.866
That ain't funny.

31:51.643 --> 31:54.908
<i>And if I never win</i>

31:56.114 --> 31:59.379
<i>'Cause this could be a feeling</i>

31:59.717 --> 32:00.979
(CLEARS THROAT)

32:01.052 --> 32:03.748
