<i>I'm sinning, too</i>

34:34.772 --> 34:37.536
<i>Just wait until the darkness falls</i>

34:37.608 --> 34:40.907
<i>so I can sin with you</i>

34:43.147 --> 34:46.241
<i>So, set out your plan</i>

34:49.253 --> 34:52.882
I had a good time tonight.
Thanks for having fun with me.

34:59.197 --> 35:02.257
- What was that for?
- Brooke was looking.

35:06.938 --> 35:10.101
