39:46.650 --> 39:50.780
<i>'Blessed are the hearts that can bend.</i>
<i>They shall never be broken. '</i>

39:53.157 --> 39:58.026
<i>But I wonder, if there's no breaking,</i>
<i>then there's no healing,</i>

