40:30.528 --> 40:35.192
<i>And I
<i>I taught myself how to grow</i></i>

40:35.266 --> 40:38.827
<i>Without any love</i>
<i>And there was poison in the rain</i>

40:38.903 --> 40:40.165
<i>I taught myself how to grow</i>

40:40.237 --> 40:41.534
