40:41.605 --> 40:44.267
<i>Now I'm crooked on the outside</i>

40:44.341 --> 40:46.969
<i>LUKE: But the struggle is a part of life.</i>

40:47.044 --> 40:48.705
- Hey.
- Hi.

40:49.914 --> 40:53.281
- I need to talk to you.
- Yeah, sure. Is everything okay?

40:53.350 --> 40:55.580
<i>So must all hearts be broken?</i>

40:55.653 --> 40:56.677
No.

